{"tid":967800,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"但願子夜不必醒","createTime":"2019-01-03T19:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T18:15:11.000Z","uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33152342aa94671d036d18f4fde20440c926b181","tid":967800,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"喜歡一個人的日子。<br />\n沒有傷亡，沒有悲喜。<br />\n直到沈淪為空間中的細小塵埃。<br />\n在落日的余暉，窗簾的罅隙中飛揚。<br />\n性格有所缺憾，無法修補。"},{"pid":"590873ee72b810771f44e276292e9c5e2024eebd","tid":967800,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"患了囈語症<br />\n喋喋不休 不明所以"},{"pid":"6b3ad2b15a3d75a7a425a691ee6bb24904f423e7","tid":967800,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:37:24.000Z","msg":"如果我也有勇氣我也要如他般踏上堅韌的步伐出去闖蕩闖蕩。可以疾馳，可以慢行。<br />\n至少知道和書本不一樣的天，不一樣的地。"},{"pid":"c27da4d64e9c478bdf178b090b813d3102a2288e","tid":967800,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:39:45.000Z","msg":"早已察覺不到日子的差異<br />\n只剩窗外的白樺又是一歲枯榮"},{"pid":"0292e5940d20748f5185922b8e4f53967d3250fc","tid":967800,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:43:27.000Z","msg":"⚔️"},{"pid":"41a8dbe81383b2056bdbf649b37c9d42057c7420","tid":967800,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:44:28.000Z","msg":"是應該浸泡在假象中獲得短暫的快樂<br />\n還是應該保持真實對事永遠冷靜"},{"pid":"1a68d64bf0918a622db424d3bd05f74fbf5e64c1","tid":967800,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T19:59:16.000Z","msg":"沒有人會介意你內心的掙扎<br />\n大家都只看自己想看到的那些東西<br />\n每說出一句話，都有無數的反駁在等待著<br />\n都在迫不及待地想要向對方證明自己才是對的<br />\n所有的交流都變成了虛偽的辯論。"},{"pid":"d7d377cb599c8a66f2db053f5a47bfcd5ba46a83","tid":967800,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T21:45:29.000Z","msg":"橙橙"},{"pid":"5faeedb7addf2e5d1433358fc356426fe2130ea3","tid":967800,"uid":13797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r